  • public class Router
extends DualMethodRouter<io.netty.channel.ChannelInboundHandler,Router>
    Targets of routes must be ChannelInboundHandler classes or instances. In case of instances, the classes of the instances must be annotated with io.netty.channel.ChannelHandler.Sharable.
